{"title":"Guilt Free","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"sugarfree-kajukatli","title":"Sugarfree Kaju Katli | Stevia Based","description":"\u003cp\u003eDadus Sugar-Free Kaju Katli offers the rich, authentic taste of traditional Kaju Katli with zero to negligible sucrose content, vetted by rigorous lab testing. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSweetened with Stevia, a natural, plant-based sweetener with a low glycemic index, these sweets are perfect for managing blood sugar levels.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith fewer calories, our sugar-free Kaju Katli is definitely a healthier choice for diabetics and diet-conscious individuals. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMade with 100% natural ingredients, Dadus sweets ensure no artificial additives, providing a delicious and healthy treat.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eWhat other Sugar Free Sweets does Dadus offer?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadus offers a variety of sugar-free sweets, including Kaju Katli, Mysore Pak, Golden Coin, Anjeer Dry Fruit Delight, Badamees, and Khajoor Coin, all crafted for a guilt-free indulgence. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eCan people with Diabetes\/Sugar eat Dadus sugar free sweets?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eAbsolutely. People with diabetes can enjoy Dadu’s sweets as they are sweetened with Stevia, suitable for blood sugar management. However, it is advisable for those with Type-1 Diabetes to consult their GP before consumption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChoose Dadu’s sugar-free sweets for a healthier treat with fewer calories and natural ingredients. Shopping for premium sweets online is easy with Dadu's. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisit Dadu’s near you for a free tasting and gourmet experience. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn Hyderabad, explore our sweets on Swiggy \u0026amp; Zomato for instant delivery. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Dadu's sweets are fresh, vegetarian, and free from preservatives or artificial colours.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45363670483224,"sku":null,"price":680.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Untitled_design_2.png?v=1755950731"},{"product_id":"sugarfree-mysore-pak","title":"Sugarfree Mysore Pak","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadus Sugar-Free Mysore Pak captures the rich, buttery essence of traditional Mysore Pak with zero to negligible sucrose content, confirmed by rigorous lab testing. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSweetened with Stevia, a natural, plant-based sweetener with a low glycemic index, our Mysore Pak is ideal for managing blood sugar levels. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith fewer calories, it is a healthier option for diet-conscious individuals. Made with 100% natural ingredients, Dadu’s Mysore Pak contains no artificial additives, ensuring a delicious and healthy treat.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eWhat other Sugar Free Sweets does Dadus offer?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadus offers a variety of sugar-free sweets, including Kaju Katli, Mysore Pak, Golden Coin, Anjeer Dry Fruit Delight, Badamees, and Khajoor Coin, all crafted for a guilt-free indulgence. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eCan people with Diabetes\/Sugar eat Dadus sugar free sweets?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbsolutely. People with diabetes can enjoy Dadu’s sweets as they are sweetened with Stevia, suitable for blood sugar management. However, it is advisable for those with Type-1 Diabetes to consult their GP before consumption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChoose Dadu’s sugar-free sweets for a healthier treat with fewer calories and natural ingredients. Shopping for premium sweets online is easy with Dadu's. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisit Dadu’s near you for a free tasting and gourmet experience. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn Hyderabad, explore our sweets on Swiggy \u0026amp; Zomato for instant delivery. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Dadu's sweets are fresh, vegetarian, and free from preservatives or artificial colours.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45363689586968,"sku":null,"price":400.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Untitled_design_1_96c393d2-350a-485e-9837-79633ca1fc7b.png?v=1755950626"},{"product_id":"sugarfree-anjeer-delight","title":"Sugarfree Anjeer Delight","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSavour the natural sweetness of figs with Dadu's Sugar-Free Anjeer Dry Fruit Delight.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThese sweets are crafted with zero to negligible sucrose, verified by rigorous lab tests, and sweetened with Stevia, a plant-based sweetener with a low glycemic index, making them perfect for managing blood sugar levels. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWith fewer calories, they are a healthier choice for diet-conscious individuals. Made from 100% natural ingredients without artificial additives, these treats ensure a delightful and nutritious experience.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eWhat other Sugar Free Sweets does Dadus offer?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadus offers a variety of sugar-free sweets, including Kaju Katli, Mysore Pak, Golden Coin, Anjeer Dry Fruit Delight, Badamees, and Khajoor Coin, all crafted for a guilt-free indulgence. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eCan people with Diabetes\/Sugar eat Dadus sugar free sweets?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbsolutely. People with diabetes can enjoy Dadu’s sweets as they are sweetened with Stevia, suitable for blood sugar management. However, it is advisable for those with Type-1 Diabetes to consult their GP before consumption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChoose Dadu’s sugar-free sweets for a healthier treat with fewer calories and natural ingredients. Shopping for premium sweets online is easy with Dadu's. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisit Dadu’s near you for a free tasting and gourmet experience. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn Hyderabad, explore our sweets on Swiggy \u0026amp; Zomato for instant delivery. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Dadu's sweets are fresh, vegetarian, and free from preservatives or artificial colours.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45363697058072,"sku":null,"price":700.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbn